<!--about-->
<section id="about" class="section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12 text-center marb-35">
        <h1 class="header-h">The PotLucky Journey</h1>
        <p class="header-p">A potluck app that allows you to coordinate who’s bringing what to an event - potluck,
          craft fair, party, convention, tailgate, whatever!
          <br>We’ve all been to that party with five bags of chips and no dessert. More dip than you know what to do
          with, but only one main dish. Way too much food, but not enough plates or silverware. Gotten to the
          convention or craft fair and *someone* forgot the folding table. Never wonder who’s bringing the kielbasa and
          who’s bringing the karaoke machine again with “PotLucky”!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-1"></div>
      <div class="col-md-10">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
          <div class="about-info">
            <h2 class="heading">Our Team</h2>
            <p>Our team is dedicated to creating a user friendly environment that will ease the stress of planning any
              event.</p>
            <div class="details-list">
              <ul>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>User friendly</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Accurate</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Creative</li>
                <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Fun!</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
          <img src="img/res01.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-1"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


